    All Classes and Interfaces

    Classes
    Class
    Description
    Capsule
    Represents a time capsule that stores a message and unlocks at a future date.
    CapsuleFileUtils
    Utility class for exporting and importing capsules to/from JSON or CSV files.
    CapsuleRepository
    Handles storing, retrieving, and managing Capsule objects using a JSON file.
    CapsuleService
    Handles business logic for managing capsules, including retrieval, deletion, restoration, and unlocking.
    DearFutureApp
    The main entry point for the Dear Future time capsule application.
    MultiThreadedMergeSort
    Multi-Threaded Merge Sort for sorting Capsules.
